OL,3,CNI civil servants offered 9% pay
OL,4,Cincrease
OL,6,FStormont's Finance Minister Caoimhe
OL,7,FArchibald has announced a 20-month pay
OL,8,Foffer for civil servants.
OL,10,FThe offer is backdated to August 1
OL,11,Flast year and covers the period up
OL,12,Funtil March 31 2026.
OL,14,FThe minister said the offer has been
OL,15,Fmade following a series of
OL,16,Fnegotiations with both industrial and
OL,17,Fnon-industrial Civil Service unions
OL,18,Fand includes a 3% consolidated
OL,19,Fincrease with effect from last August
OL,20,Fand a 6% consolidated increase with
OL,21,Feffect from August 2025.
