OL,6,FMs Archibald said: "I am committed to
OL,7,Fensuring civil servants receive pay
OL,8,Fwhich recognises the valuable role
OL,9,Fthey play in public service delivery.
OL,11,F"This 20-month offer is a first step
OL,12,Ftowards longer-term pay deals giving
OL,13,Fcertainty to workers.
OL,15,F"The pay offer made today is a
OL,16,Fpositive one that I hope will be well
OL,17,Freceived by staff and unions.
