OL,3,CNI civil servants offered 9% pay
OL,4,Cincrease
OL,6,F"Given the current budgetary
OL,7,Fchallenges, I regret that I am unable
OL,8,Fto make a higher pay offer for 2024
OL,9,Fthat is at the same level as other
OL,10,Fpublic sector workers."
OL,12,FShe added: "Transformation of our
OL,13,Fpublic services will require the
OL,14,Fexpertise of our staff.
OL,16,F"This offer if accepted would mean the
OL,17,Fmajority of civil servants eligible
OL,18,Ffor both pay awards will receive at
OL,19,Fleast 9% increase on salaries over the
OL,20,F20 months recognising their vital work
OL,21,Fin delivering public services here."
